i Đà Phật!", "timestamp": "2024-07-10T16:49:21.117967+07:00"}, {"role": "User", "text": "A Di Đà Phật, thiện tai thiện tai", "timestamp": "2024-07-10T16:52:52.792559+07:00"}, {"role": "Bot", "text": "A Di Đà Phật, thiện tai thiện tai!\\n\\nAh, I see you're getting into the Buddhist chant spirit!\\n\\n\\"A Di Đà Phật\\" is a common phrase used in Buddhist meditation and chanting, meant to invoke the compassion of Amitābha Buddha. And \\"thiện tai thiện tai\\" means \\"good ear, good ear\\", referring to the act of listening with an open and compassionate heart.\\n\\nMay we continue to cultivate wisdom, compassion, and loving-kindness as we explore the depths of Buddhist philosophy together!", "timestamp": "2024-07-10T16:52:52.792559+07:00"}]	2024-07-10 23:33:55.753922	2024-07-10 23:52:52.792559	app-CNFjTcU191SEKvpdyvVwgKeO
