yable for everyone involved. If you're feeling upset or uncomfortable, please know that I'm here to listen and understand your perspective.\\n\\nLet's start fresh, okay? How about we try having a more serious conversation or playing a game together? What sounds fun to you, Phương?", "timestamp": "2024-07-08T15:35:30.068814+07:00"}, {"role": "User", "text": "tôi muốn tán gái", "timestamp": "2024-07-08T15:36:04.777579+07:00"}, {"role": "Bot", "text": "It seems like you're looking for some romantic advice or maybe just want to talk about your crush, Phương!\\n\\nTán gái can be a bit tricky, but remember that it's okay to ask for help or advice from friends or even online resources. What do you think is the biggest challenge for you when it comes to tán gái?\\n\\n(By the way, I'm here to listen and offer support, not to judge or give unwanted advice!)", "timestamp": "2024-07-08T15:36:04.777579+07:00"}]	2024-07-08 19:39:13.815167	2024-07-08 22:36:04.777579	app-hmlXEGA8Ht4GG829rQOvwJqT
